    %h1 Payments: Cancel
    %hr

.row
  .col-sm-12
    %p This API allows you to cancel a payment given a specific id.

    .note.note-danger
      %strong Note:
      This is a <a href="/sections/api/authorization.html">Token Authorized</a> call.


    %h4 Cancel a Payment

    %pre
      %code
        POST https://app.sign2pay.com/api/v2/purchases/55fac963e6db9909ba000003/cancel

    %h4 Request Headers &amp; Body
    %pre
      %code
        :preserve
          Accept: */*
          Accept-Encoding: gzip, deflate
          Content-Type: application/json
          Authorization: Token token=2d7c34be6b03de66386e50a962dd4349
          Accept-Language: en-us

    %h4 Response Body
    %pre
      %code
        :preserve
          {
            "message": "Purchase successfully cancelled"
          }

